{
  "stem": "1183.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they pushed me up, and let's go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From then on, we went to, successively, two camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And actually, not camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were not actually concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were just barracks where they could put us up for the night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then we-- how we started to go by car-- by cattle car, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After that walk, we went from one [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sleeping place-- put it that way-- to another.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We came on one, and it was called Bendorf.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a salt mine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there I met my-- met the mother of my girlfriend and were we to see, but I lost her again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We left-- we left that camp, then after a couple of days again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they took-- the Germans took-- emptied the camp and took all kinds of clothes invested with lice onto us and we had to carry it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were also Gypsies left the camp, and they were with us on the transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then that was a transport there-- from there to another place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was a woman there, the wife of a Dutch comedian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Gypsies were positioned by the Germans into the cattle car as to-- so they could do the dirty work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had to do the dirty work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know-- the Gypsies had displeasure with the woman, maybe didn't like her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she was in the wagon next to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They tortured her to death with putting drops of water or letting it subtly as the woman screams and screams.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the scream of the woman was-- for days, was horrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Well, finally, naturally, they killed her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I had to sit with the Gypsies too once, because-- I don't know what I did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was punishment, so they pushed and they pummeled me.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
